{"tid":720153,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[喂呀!]傳暗撻3個月 江嘉敏出招冧掂余德丞","createTime":"2018-06-27T17:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T05:30:42.000Z","uid":5190,"like":9,"dislike":263,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"313d846674d6c0b00943a731bb7ba5bfc57f8bbb","tid":720153,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3Tst65gi9IE0NkQ3agTAuw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180627f134841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3Tst65gi9IE0NkQ3agTAuw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180627f134841.jpg&h=b1a64f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】入行只有3年的無綫力捧小花江嘉敏，每齣劇都會與合作的小生傳出緋聞，異性緣極強。新一期《東周刊》報道，江嘉敏因拍新劇《危城First Lady》，與超級「筍盤」余德丞戲假情真，並已暗撻3個月。<br />\n<br />\n身為前香港游泳代表隊成員的余德丞是「巨胸小鮮肉」，跟父母一家三口居於跑馬地大坑道嘉園，一個市值近2千萬的豪宅單位，再加上家人手持的其他物業，總市值逾半億元。<br />\n<br />\n據片場工作人員透露，江嘉敏不時請零食及送上靚湯冧掂余德丞，男方則日日做「柴可夫」管接送，甜蜜滿瀉。二人在劇中有感情線，奉旨談情，更不避嫌在社交平台上載「蜜照」，兼公開打情罵俏。"},{"pid":"761b55501504284e7c129aa8bdebeda1541b758e","tid":720153,"uid":74435,"like":147,"dislike":1,"score":146,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"喂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c156396d9b277405d02ff2b9dc7702be30fdc6","tid":720153,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:49:00.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"4ac57b3a5134d00208db09855d7725a217997c18","tid":720153,"uid":7903,"like":405,"dislike":2,"score":403,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:54:41.000Z","msg":"條仔慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知道呢條女咩底細"},{"pid":"8d76bee22fb15b9c9fac24b5f03ca444066d30dd","tid":720153,"uid":62815,"like":93,"dislike":9,"score":84,"citedB